  <bioghist id="aspace_d61515aff84f5ff4045aabd0218f9b69">
    <head>History</head>
<p>The Port Authority of Allegheny County was created in 1956 by the Pennsylvania State Legislature; in 1959 the legislature allowed the Authority to purchase and consolidate privately-owned trasportation companies that were providing transportation services throughout Allegheny County. The companies were officially acquired in 1963 and the Port Authority began service in March 1964.</p>  </bioghist>
