  <scopecontent id="aspace_fb8122c96a3dff9dd0297d577658a4ad">
    <head>Scope and Content Notes</head>
<p>Press releases from the Port Authority of Allegheny County that detail the operational and administrative changes the organization went through from 1977 until 1985. Folders consist of press releases detailing construction projects, peronnel changes, system-wide changes and innovations, and other notices regarding the Port Authority's transit services and leadership.</p>  </scopecontent>
